About this property

Located in Snowmass Village, Mountain Chalet Snowmass features guestrooms with free WiFi, as well as a pool and a free airport shuttle. Buttermilk Ski Area is a 20-minute drive, while Aspen Mountain is a 30-minute drive from the property. At the resort each room includes a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with free toiletries, while some boast mountain views. Guests at Mountain Chalet Snowmass can take part in various activities in the surroundings, including skiing, snowboarding and cycling. Alpine Springs is 0.6 mi from the accommodations. The nearest airport is Aspen-Pitkin County Airport, 5 mi from the property and Denver International Airport is 224 mi away.

Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 9.5 for a two-person trip.
